video: s3c-fb: use ARCH_ dependancy

Use ARCH_ dependancy when using s3c-fb.  S3C_DEV_FB, S5P_DEV_FIMD0 cannot
be enabled on EXYNOS5.  So, ARCH_ should be used as dependancy for s3c-fb.

